      "id": "92632938ba8160d13c925992",
      "engagement_type": "MEETING",
      "body": "On-site walkthrough with Karen to plan winter seasonal refresh. North entrance needs the spent ginger replaced, going with yellow heliconia. Karen wants the oceanfront path cleaned and mulched before the holiday rush. Crew scheduled for three full days late October.",
      "contact_ids": [
        "063bf6966b9ea1fdb5597c94"
      ],
      "company_ids": [
        "ef831fc564f7a8d222e0cb71"
      ],
      "title": "Winter prep walkthrough",
      "description": null,
      "phone": null,
      "createdate": "2025-09-15T00:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ebaceb17baa68f6ca8b7445a",
      "engagement_type": "CALL",
      "body": "Summer check-in call with Karen. Resort is busy with tourist season, grounds holding up well. The heliconia near the north entrance needs thinning before it overtakes the walkway. Karen mentioned her husband just retired from Pearl Harbor naval base and they're planning a trip to Japan in September. She asked about doing something special for the resort's 15th anniversary in August, maybe a Hawaiian native plant display near the entrance. Said she'd get budget approval. Karen always brings mochi from that bakery in Kaimuki when we do on-site meetings, best mochi on the island.",
      "contact_ids": [
        "063bf6966b9ea1fdb5597c94"
      ],
      "company_ids": [
        "ef831fc564f7a8d222e0cb71"
      ],
      "title": "Summer season check-in",
      "description": null,
      "phone": "(808) 555-7815",
      "createdate": "2025-06-15T00:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "bedb2f638cdac37bad067e2e",
      "engagement_type": "NOTE",
      "body": "Year-end walkthrough with Karen at Turtle Bay. Oceanfront path mulching looks great, yellow heliconia from the winter refresh is starting to bloom. Karen is thrilled. She mentioned her son Kai is getting married in March at a North Shore venue and asked if we could consult on ceremony flowers. Told her PG doesn't do event floral but I'd ask around. She said the resort holiday party is December 18 and wants the entrance looking perfect by then. Ordered extra white ginger for the front gardens. Karen's favorite Mother's Day lei is tuberose, she wants to plant some near the spa entrance next spring.",
      "contact_ids": [
        "063bf6966b9ea1fdb5597c94"
      ],
      "company_ids": [
        "ef831fc564f7a8d222e0cb71"
      ],
      "title": "Year-end property walkthrough",
      "description": null,
      "phone": null,
      "createdate": "2025-11-25T00:00:00Z"
    }
  ]
}

